When the terrorist suffered a misfire, a patron tackled him, which made him drop his main firearm. This was followed by other people pursuing the terrorist, and ended with him pinned down on the side of the street, as can be seen in the video.

The police formally cancelled the pride parade due to increased threat levels.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RRAX7L9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Despite this, hundreds of people marched in Oslo, chanting: "We're here, we're queer, we won't disappear!" the morning after.

Bjarne Finsrud, the patron who first attacked the terrorist, is scheduled to receive the Norwegian medal of noble deed in gold.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/onf25xr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheAnswerWasAlwaysMoreLube]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Silky anteater cute af</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/w99NZTf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LvVNh4Y.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/w99NZTf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[IamJACKSventedSPLEEN]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Pure carnage</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/apCZm3d</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/odrP3CA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/apCZm3d</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GravityVT]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's ok to laugh. It's weird, I think sometimes we forget it's ok to be happy while we're struggling.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nB0ANvX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zV3g2e2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So, like, laugh and stuff. Or at stuff. But not at folks, unless they're, ya know what? Just live your lives.

